frontend->cartservice/AddItem`: 5.2x latency increase (3785ms → 19538ms)\n   - `checkoutservice->cartservice/EmptyCart`: 3.7x latency increase (2258ms → 8423ms)\n\n2. **Product Catalog Service Baseline High Latency**: While the latency increase during the anomaly period is modest (1.2x), the baseline normal duration is already very high (~10s), suggesting this service may have underlying performance issues.\n\n3. **Frontend Internal Operations Affected**: The `frontend->frontend/CartService/AddItem` operation shows a 4.0x latency increase, indicating that the frontend service itself is experiencing resource contention or processing delays.\n\n**Root Cause Analysis:**\nThe cart service appears to be the primary root cause based on:\n- Largest latency multiplier (5.2x)\n- Affects multiple upstream services (frontend and checkoutservice)\n- Consistent across different operations (AddItem and EmptyCart)\n\nThe product catalog service, while showing high baseline latency, may be a contributing factor but appears to be more of a secondary issue compared to the cart service's dramatic performance degradation.", "metric_analysis_findings": "基于收集到的指标数据，我现在进行故障分析。从指标数据中可以看到多个异常情况，我将按照优先级进行分析。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"node_filesystem_usage_rate\", \"node_memory_usage_rate\", \"node_cpu_usage_rate\", \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes\", \"rrt_max\", \"rrt\", \"pod_cpu_usage\", \"error_ratio\", \"client_error_ratio\", \"io_util\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-05\",\n      \"reason\": \"节点文件系统使用率显著升高，node_filesystem_usage_rate从25.2%上升到66.64%，变化率90.23%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"node_filesystem_usage_rate: 正常中位数25.2% → 故障中位数66.64%，P99从36.0%上升到97.55%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-04\",\n      \"reason\": \"节点内存使用率异常，node_memory_usage_rate从30.0%上升到42.53%，同时node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes下降\",\n      \"evidence\": \"node_memory_usage_rate: 30.0% → 42.53%(变化率34.55%)，MemAvailable_bytes从